Package it.polimi.ingsw.model.cards

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Card
    Main abstract class inherited by cards classes.
    DevelopmentCard
    Development card class
    LeaderCard
    If the card is initially unflipped it means it's on its face at the begging, it can't be used, isFlipped=false; When a card isFlipped it can be used.
    LeaderCardCost
    This class is used to exemplify the cost of a development card, especially useful when checking the activation cost of a leader card that needs development cards in order to be activated.
    LorenzoCard
    Lorenzo's cards are the six action cards used during the single player game
